---
title: Decorator Pattern — Service Layer
---
classDiagram
    class IFundService {
        <<interface>>
        +findAll(params) Result~PaginatedResponse~
        +findById(id) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +create(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +update(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
    }

    class FundService {
        -fundRepo: IFundRepository
        +findAll(params) Result~PaginatedResponse~
        +findById(id) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +create(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +update(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
    }

    class LoggingFundService {
        -fundService: IFundService
        -logger: ILogger
        +findAll(params) Result~PaginatedResponse~
        +findById(id) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +create(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +update(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
    }

    class CachingFundService {
        -fundService: IFundService
        -cache: ICacheService
        -logger: ILogger
        +findAll(params) Result~PaginatedResponse~
        +findById(id) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +create(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
        +update(data) Result~FundResponseDto~
    }

    class FundController {
        -service: IFundService
        +listFunds(req, res)
        +getFund(req, res)
        +createFund(req, res)
        +updateFund(req, res)
    }

    IFundService <|.. FundService : implements
    IFundService <|.. LoggingFundService : implements
    IFundService <|.. CachingFundService : implements

    LoggingFundService o-- FundService : wraps
    CachingFundService o-- LoggingFundService : wraps

    FundController --> IFundService : depends on\n(injected as TOKENS.FundService)

    note for CachingFundService "Outermost layer.\nShort-circuits on cache hit —\nLoggingFundService never called."
    note for LoggingFundService "Times the inner call.\nLogs success / error / slow query."
    note for FundService "Pure business logic.\nNo caching or logging."
